===Verb===
'''haista'''

# to [[smell]] or [[stink]], to emit an [[odor]]
# [[sniff]]! Imperative case of [[haistaa]], as in [[haistattelu]]

Also used like this: ''Etkö haista palaneen käryä?'' Don't you smell something burning?

